meta.description: Based on its elevated antioxidant levels, organic foods may be considered 20 to 40 percent healthier, the equivalent of adding one or two servings’ worth to a five-a-day regimen. Find out about the latest nutrition research on organic foods, delivered in free, easy to understand videos.

title: Organic Foods: The Latest Research
cleaned_text: One of the few food contaminants found at higher levels in those eating plant-based diets are mycotoxins, fungal toxins in moldy food ingredients, such as oats.
